SOME NPM CLI COMMENTS
1)npm install--save package-ko-naam //installs the package locally on your project
2)npm install -g package-ko-naam//installs the package globally in your machine
3)npm uninstall --save package-ko-naam //!1
4)npm uninstall --g package-ko-naam//!2